description         Fast JSON parser and serializer for Nim
long_description    Jsony is a loose, direct to object JSON parser and serializer \
                    for Nim. It is designed to be fast and flexible, allowing \
                    parsing of JSON into Nim objects with minimal boilerplate. \
                    It supports relaxed JSON syntax, custom hooks and efficient \
                    serialization/deserialization of complex data structures.

